What does our bank product information look like?

SELECT *
FROM bank_products;


What product names have a checking or savings account?

SELECT product_name
FROM bank_products
WHERE product_type="Checking"
OR
product_type="Savings";


What product names have a Savings product type and have an interest_rate of at least 0.75, and have no monthly fee?

SELECT monthly_fee, product_type, interest_rate, product_name
FROM bank_products
WHERE product_type="Savings"
AND
interest_rate > 0.75
AND
monthly_fee = 0
